2 Installation
**************

Install the binary package with:

     sudo apt install ./clamdscan-tools_0.1.0_all.deb

   Remove it with:

     sudo apt remove clamdscan-tools

   Purge the package, including configuration files managed by dpkg,
with:

     sudo apt purge clamdscan-tools


